You fetch the data asynchronously so after the data is received and you update the grid with it, you need to tell the change detector to check for changes.

You do this by adding this to your code:

1. Add the change detector injection to your constructor

        constructor(private entidadesService: EntidadesService, private changeDetector: ChangeDetectorRef) {}

2. Ask the change detector to check for changes:

        fromAPI() {
            this.entidadesService.get().subscribe(entidades =&gt; {
                this.gridData = entidades;
                //   this.onFilter(&#39;asd&#39;);

                // Ask the change detector to check for changes at the earliest convenience
                this.changeDetector.markForCheck();
            });
        }

