The `.selectthis` elements are not siblings so to get the index of them related to each other you need to provide a selector to `index()` to find the current element within, eg. `index(&#39;.selectthis&#39;)`

Also note that the index of an element is zero-based, so the third element would return an index of `2`. As such you need to add one to the value to get the output you want. Try this:

